snippet.textDisplay: This has to be in my top three from Coke Studio. ❤ I must have listened to this hundreds of times, but today again it was full on goose bumps. These 2 brothers are just brilliant - Javed Bashir and Akbar Ali have such different styles but both are masters of classical music in their own rights. There’s so much to appreciate in this whole production - the arrangement (by classic ghazal singer Nayyara Noor’s son Jaffar Zaidi); Aamir Zaki’s solo up there on that pedestal...almost like he’s looking down upon us lesser mortals from Heaven above; the sheer contrast between the drums and the saarangi and the fluidity with which the song evolves from classical to qawali to rock and back! Have to say you girls have such good choice in music! Even at this young age you have the ability to appreciate the nuances of all genres (from rap to classical) and are obviously well versed with technical know-how and have experienced it all! Loved, loved this reaction - thank you for showing so much love, respect, adoration, passion, sensitivity and knowledge...this masterpiece definitely deserved it all! 🙏🏻❤
